UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2598
1 Kentucky:
2 Section 1. The Senate hereby recognizes September 10, 2026, through
3 November 1, 2026, as a voluntary time of prayer, fasting, and reflection in connection
4 with the Nehemiah Alliance National 52-Day Rebuild Initiative.
5 Section 2. The Senate encourages all Kentuckians who so choose to participate
6 in this solemn and hopeful call for spiritual renewal, unity, and national restoration by
7 joining the National Nehemiah Alliance at www.na52.org.
8 Section 3. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transmit copies of this
9 Resolution to Senator Lindsey Tichenor for delivery to the Nehemiah Alliance.
